        {
            "+content": "Rinko Nakama is a 24-year-old office worker who is a huge anime fan. She lives next door to two men: Akito Satsuki, a handsome man who acts sweetly around her, and Haruma Usada, a hot-headed man who seems to be irritated with her love for anime. After a certain incident, the three's apartments become connected through holes in the wall. This leads to Rinko's life becoming more complicated than usual.",
